# Premium Light Theme Redesign: Deep Blue & Ash

Complete color scheme migration from dark mode to a premium light theme with deep blue accents and ash/grey backgrounds. Also includes realtime server hardening for always-on connectivity.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Auth Screens (Login, Register, Splash, Welcome):** These currently have dramatic dark gradients that create a strong first impression. We have two options:
> 1. **Keep dark auth screens** — Login/splash stays dark/dramatic, main app is light. This creates a nice contrast.
> 2. **Full light everywhere** — Auth screens also become light with deep blue accents.
>
> **Which do you prefer?**

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **TopBar (Header) Color:** Two premium options:
> 1. **Deep Navy Blue header** (`#1e3a8a`) with white text — Bold, authoritative, like a banking app.
> 2. **White header** with deep blue text/icons — Clean, minimalist, like Apple's design.
>
> **Recommendation:** Deep navy header for a more distinctive, branded feel. Which do you prefer?

