### Phase 6: Realtime Server Hardening (1 file)

#### [MODIFY] [socket.ts](file:///d:/suzuzy_web_site/servicestuff-rn/services/socket.ts)

Make the realtime connection "always on":

1. **Infinite reconnection:**
```diff
-reconnectionAttempts: 10,
-reconnectionDelay: 2000,
+reconnectionAttempts: Infinity,
+reconnectionDelay: 1000,
+reconnectionDelayMax: 30000,
```

2. **AppState awareness** — Reconnect when app comes to foreground:
```typescript
import { AppState } from 'react-native';

// In connect():
AppState.addEventListener('change', (state) => {
  if (state === 'active' && this.currentStaffId && !this.socket?.connected) {
    this.reconnect();
  }
});
```

3. **Periodic health check** — Ping every 30s, reconnect if dead:
```typescript
private healthCheckInterval: NodeJS.Timeout | null = null;

startHealthCheck() {
  this.healthCheckInterval = setInterval(() => {
    if (this.currentStaffId && !this.socket?.connected) {
      this.reconnect();
    }
  }, 30000);
}
```

4. **Network listener** — Reconnect when internet comes back:
```typescript
import NetInfo from '@react-native-community/netinfo';

NetInfo.addEventListener(state => {
  if (state.isConnected && this.currentStaffId && !this.socket?.connected) {
    this.reconnect();
  }
});
```

