## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npx tsc --noEmit` after each phase to ensure no type errors
- Visual check each screen on both Android and iOS simulators

### Manual Verification
- Test in bright daylight conditions (the primary use case for technicians)
- Verify text contrast ratios meet WCAG AA (4.5:1 for normal text)
- Check socket reconnection by toggling airplane mode on/off
- Verify the app reconnects socket when brought from background to foreground
